Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.39,0:24:01.39,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1437394,1441398}The Yagisawa sisters skip the match with Korea\Nbecause of their mother's death.{NOTE:母の死で親善試合出場を断念した八木沢三姉妹。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.39,0:24:06.07,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1441398,1446070}Kozue, trying to live up to their expectations,\Nparticipates and uses her injured wrist.{NOTE:こずえは彼女たちの期待を担えつつ負傷した手首をかばって出場した。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.07,0:24:08.69,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1446070,1448697}But, as expected,\Nthe improvised team shows its flaws.{NOTE:だがやはりにわか仕立ての混成チーム…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:12.61,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1448697,1452618}The players show lack of discipline and cooperation.{NOTE:…各選手はそれぞれの思いを露骨に表し淫らに乱れた。}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.61,0:24:17.66,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1452618,1457665}The Japanese team barely wins the first set,\Nmostly owing to Kozue's selfless attack.{NOTE:その時こずえの捨て身の攻撃で日本チームはかろうじて第一セットを取ったが…}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.66,0:24:21.46,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1457665,1461460}But as a result, Kozue goes to warm the bench.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.46,0:24:25.46,Alternative,Narrator,0,0,0,,{TIME:1461460,1465464}Please look forward to the next episode.
